cs.HC, cs.CR, cs.GR, cs.CY, cs.SI 

The paper focuses on providing interactive visualizations for post-game feedback in serious cybersecurity games, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The visualizations are designed to be easy to decode for players, which involves graphics (cs.GR) and visualization (cs.SI). Finally, the paper evaluates the usability of the visualizations in a field study, which involves cybersecurity (cs.CY) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
